by hooverine
There was something she said that stayed with me. So well put. &lsquo;When he leads a step, say backwards for the woman&rsquo;, Graciela said, &lsquo;then there is one possibility: going backwards. There are not three possible steps. Not three, not two. One.&rsquo;
All the time I see so called &lsquo;advanced&rsquo; dancers, throwing their partners around, the women looking like nervous chicken trying to guess the right thing to do for each and every step.
